title: Cant switch regions
body: What time can i switch regions? been waiting for a couple months now... {{champion:32}}

replies.body:
Those account transfers should be back up on Nov 20!

EDIT: Looks like those transfers didn't make it back on the scheduled date for some reason. The status page mentions they were down while ranked rewards were going out, so they should be back up very shortly!
